ible=true. Meaningful tests can start an in-process Vert.x HttpServer on 127.0.0.1 and exercise WebClient requests, JSON/form/multipart bodies, caching, cookies, redirects, and streaming without Docker or external services.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Without the unsafe-access runtime property, native execution can fail in Netty allocation code with PlatformDependent0.safeConstructPutInt / connection-closed cascades.\",\n    \"The artifact declares optional io.vertx:vertx-auth-oauth2; only add it if tests intentionally target OAuth2-specific APIs, not for core WebClient coverage.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_056047943254ccea016a3e9e82ff908195a6c2e42209e592e7\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1226, "output": 601, "cacheRead": 36352, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 38179, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782488699844, "responseId": "resp_056047943254ccea016a3e9e7c49cc8195ae90d233d681ab92"}}
